item.title: About
item.description: Hey there, My name is Syed Zoheb Ali Sumair. I have been working on the web technologies for more than 5 years but i am still learning alot of things as web is evolving and so are we. Along the way I found a passion for interaction design & front-end development, and I use those passions to create interfaces that solve problems. When I’m not creating beautiful solutions, I enjoy reading Books, exercising and also an amateur photographer.
